programme.title: Drama On 2 – Sherry Supir Ep1
programme.desc: Drama komedi 13 episod ini memaparkan kisah seorang ibu tunggal, Sherry yang menjadi pemandu e-panggilan. Setelah bercerai dan diberhentikan kerja sejak tiga tahun lalu, Sherry bekerja keras untuk menyara ibu, anaknya yang berusia 10 tahun serta adiknya yang masih belajar di institusi pengajian tinggi. Dalam melaksanakan tugas hariannya, Sherry bertemu dengan pelbagai jenis penumpang yang mempunyai pelbagai masalah dan ragam hidup.

programme.title: Drama On 2 – Enjoy Your Stay Ep13/EpAkhir
programme.desc: Kehilangan Tuan Rudi sudah menjadi buah mulut pekerja Damai Beach Resort. Tiba-tiba pekerja am Sean dan Beber diangkat menjadi pengurus segera kerana mereka yang paling lama berkhidmat di Damai Beach Resort selain Kak Maggie yang sudah amnesia. Sean dan Beber mempunyai dua sikap yang berbeza namun mereka perlu bersama-sama menjadi pengurus hotel untuk menyelamatkan hotel tersebut sementara menunggu kepulangan Tuan Rudi dan mendapatkan gaji mereka yang tertunggak. Kak Maggie seorang wanita cina yang buat kerja seperti sloth tetapi tahu tentang semua kedudukan kewangan hotel. Tuan Rudi pula telah melarikan diri kerana dia dikejar oleh Ah Long kerana tidak mampu membayar hutang.

programme.title: Hiburan On 2 – Konsert Minggu Ini (Ukays Reunion)
programme.desc: Saksikan kembali persembahan istimewa kumpulan Ukays dalam konsert terbitan Unit Hiburan TV, RTM.

programme.title: Asian On 2 – Tere Bina Jiya Jaye Naa Ep54
programme.desc: Kisah mengenai Krisha, seorang graduan hospitaliti yang cuba sedaya upaya untuk membuktikan dirinya dan membantu keluarganya dari segi kewangan dengan bekerja di hotel diraja rakan bapanya, di Udaipur. Kehidupan Krisha amat sempurna dan bahagia apabila dia berkahwin dengan cintanya, Devraj. Walaubagaimanapun,tidaklama kemudian, dia mendapati dirinya terjebak dalam kehidupan yang penuh dengan pembohongandanpenipuan.

programme.title: Hiburan On 2 – Asian Culture Ep11
programme.desc: Bersama Soo Winci dalam program yang memaparkan sejarah, budaya dan masyarakat serta keunikan tempat pelancongan yang menarik dan popular di negaranegara Asia.

programme.title: Drama On 2 – Mukhlis (Siri 1) Ep25
programme.desc: Haikal, pemuda yang memiliki sebuah syarikat pengiklanan. Satu hari Haikal terjatuh dari tangga rumahnya. Dia telah dimasukkan ke hospital. programme.title: Religious Clip S32 Ep3

Tetapi detik damainya di sana tidak bertahan lama, Ezgi, Ozan dan Deniz pergi mencarinya. Setiap saat dia berkongsi dengannya, dia menyedari bahawa dia tidak boleh tanpanya dan melamar Ezgi. Ezgi akhirnya menjalani impiannya, mencari cinta sejati. Dia mengiyakan cadangannya untuk bahagia selamanya dengan zgr.

programme.title: Hanya Tuhan Yang Tahu
programme.desc: Ramlan dan Maria membawa anak perempuannya, Shazlin untuk tinggal bersama mereka demi keselamatan Shazlin. Dia telah dipukul oleh Along kerana suaminya, Iskandar berhutang. Shazlin hanya diam tetapi tertekan dengan permasalahan itu. Ramlan pula bersimpati pada Iskandar dan ingin membantunya menyelesaikan hutang Iskandar dengan Along. Tetapi dalam masa yang sama, Ramlan memasang perangkap adakah benar Iskandar berhutang dengan Along.

programme.title: Maria Terindah S1 Ep20
programme.desc: Aris yang bekerja dia Miri, bercadang untuk menghabiskan cuti bersama teman baiknya, Fahad menikmati keindahan alam semulajadi di Hutan Simpan Mulu Sarawak. Sementara itu, Jihan dan Maria yang baru selesai mendaki Gunung Santubong, bercadang untuk melanjutkan percutian mereka ke Mulu sebelum pulang ke Kuala Lumpur. Mereka berempat mula bertemu sewaktu berada di Mulu. Pertemuan pertama kali membuatkan Aris jatuh cinta dengan Maria, dan dalam masa yang sama, menyedari yang Fahad juga menyukai Maria. Malangnya, Jihan dar awal memang tida menyukai dua orang lelaki yang baginya hanya menyusahkan itu. Sepanjang ekspedisi mereka, Jihan yang sentiasa berperanan sebagai seorang kakak nampak kurang senang apabila Maria kerap melayan Aris dan Fahad. Sedikit situasi berlaku di dalam Gua Mulu mengakibatkan Jihan tercedera dan tidak dapat ikut serta pada ekspedisi mereka keesokan hari. Disebabkan terlalu geram dan menyalahkan Fahad atas apa yang berlaku, Fahad juga ditahan dari ikut serta ekspedisi yang akan dijalankan. Akhrinya, hanya Maria dan Aris bersama beberapa orang pengunjung lain yang menyertai ekspedisi tersebut. Di dalam hutan, kerana terlalu teruja dan leka, Maria tersesat dan terpisah dari orang lain. Nasibnya baik kerana Aris ada untuk menyelamatkannya, tetapi mereka akhirnya dapati yang mereka berdua telah sama sama sesat di dalan hutan itu. Aris melindungi Maria sepanjang masa mereka di dalam hutan itu sehingga hari gelap. Dan tiba tiba pada malam hari, mereka diserang dan Aris disumpit.

programme.desc: Memaparkan Hani semasa berada di kampung bukan sahaja menjaga Sheila dan anaknya, tetapi menguruskan rumah tangga bersama ibunya. Di hujung minggu Mizan juga pulang. Mizan menunjukkan hubungan dia dengan Hani mesra. Hani secara ikhlas juga menunjukkan mesranya mereka berdua. Walau pun begitu mereka tidak sempat bersama sebagai suami isteri, bererti sejak mereka berkahwin masih berkeadaan sedemikian kerana di Kuala Lumpur pun mereka tinggal di bilik berasingan. Kesempatan Mizan dapat berbual ringkas dengan Hani, Mizan memberi amaran kepada Hani supaya sentiasa menunjukkanhubungan mereka kepada kedua-dua ibu bapa sebagai tidak ada masalah apa-apa pun. Hani akur, Kebetulan anak Sheila tidak sihat membuatkan semasa Mizan hendak pulang ke Kuala Lumpur, Hani tidak turut serta. Semasa Mizan hendak pulang, kedua-dua mereka "beraksi", pura-pura baik dan mesra kerana ibu dan bapa mereka ada bersama. Sheila kini bukan sahaja berterima kasih kepada Sheila tetapi dia juga menceritakan Nizam seorang yang baik, sanggup menerimanya. Dia juga menanti Nizam dengan penuh mengharap menerimanya. Selain itu menyatakan ibu dan bapanya mungkin akan bertambah marah apabila dapat tahu dia telah melahirkan anak. Mizan selepas tiba di Kuala Lumpur kelihatan kurang ceria dan menjadi kehairanan kepada Zul.

programme.desc: Sepanjang berada di UK, Farah diasak rindu terhadap Lukman dan Zahin. Dia sibukkan diri dengan studi demi melupakan segala kemelut yang melanda di samping menjaga kandungannya yang makin membesar. Farah tidak tahu bahawa Lukman ditahan di lokap. Berita kematian Mama akibat heart attack bukan sahaja merentap jiwanya, malah meragut seluruh kebahagiaan keluarga. Lukman dihambat penyesalan tak berkesudahan. Zulkarnain ikat jamin dan menyelesaikan segala tuntutan syarikat untuk membebaskan Lukman. Liza dan Nazim seumpama tulang belakang yang sentiasa menyokong Farah di Manchester. Farah terkejut apabila Lukman tiba-tiba muncul di depan pintu apartment untuk memohon maaf kepadanya. Farah tidak sanggup berdepan dengan Lukman hingga menyebabkan mereka bertengkar. Tanpa sengaja, Farah tergelincir dan terjatuh di tangga hingga mengalami pendarahan

programme.title: Jendela Hati Ep09
programme.desc: Pejabat Lukman diceroboh masuk oleh lelaki yang tidak dikenali. Lukman balik dalam keadaan marah-marah setelah mendapat hantaran foto Farah bersama Anas. Lukman diamuk cemburu hingga langsung tidak mempercayai kata-kata Farah. Perbalahan mereka didengari Kak Yati dan Papa. Makan malam yang dirancang menjadi muram dan tidak seindah dirancang. Tanpa diduga, Zulkarnain balik membawa sebiji kek untuk meraikan hari lahir Farah. Lukman terkesima dan malu kerana dia sebagai suami tidak mengingati hari lahir Farah. Ego membuatkan dia tercabar dengan sambutan familinya terhadap Farah. Farah pulang ke kampung untuk meraikan hari kelahirannya di kuburan arwah Sarah. Lukman sanggup menggunakan duit insuran arwah Sarah yang diamanahkan kepada Zahin untuk dipinjamkan kepada Myra. Mama pula jatuh pengsan di rumah. Keadaan Mama membuatkan Kak Yati mengajak Farah tinggal bersama apatah lagi Lukman ada kerja di Pulau Pinang.

programme.title: Jendela Hati Ep10
programme.desc: Farah terkejut melihat sepasang kasut perempuan di luar pintu rumah Lukman. Farah hilang sabar dan naik hantu sebaik melihat Myra ada di ruang tamu. Farah dengan Myra bertengkar. Namun, Farah lebih sentap apabila Lukman seakan menyebelahi Myra. Kak Yati seakan tidak percaya dengan aduan Farah dan menganggap ada salah faham. Farah minta Kak Yati rahsiakan segalanya demi kesihatan Mama. Hati Farah makin sakit melihat sikap hipokrit Lukman di hadapan famili seolah-olah tiada apa-apa yang berlaku. Farah terkejut apabila doktor mengesahkan dia hamil. Lebih membuatkan dia teruja apabila permohonannya untuk melanjutkan pengajian di peringkat Master juga diluluskan. Dalam teruja, hatinya tetap berbelah bahagi apabila memikirkan Zahin. Lukman pula disyaki terlibat dalam kehilangan wang syarikat.

programme.title: Gila Baby
programme.desc: Bob memerlukan wang yang banyak bagi membiayai kos pembedahan ayahnya di hospital. Dengan mengambil jalan mudah, Bob membantu Roy, bekas teman sekelasnya di sekolah yang selalu membulinya dahulu untuk melakukan jenayah mencuri kereta. Walaupun percubaan pertama Bob untuk aktiviti jenayah tersebut berjaya tetapi ada seorang bayi di tempat duduk belakang kereta yang dicurinya itu! Bob kini mendapati dirinya diburu oleh beberapa pihak yang tidak akan berhenti selagi Bob dan bayi tersebut tidak ditangkap! Untuk mengeruhkan lagi keadaan, dalam perjalanan menyelamatkan diri, Bob bertemu Jaja yang mengugut Bob untuk membawanya sekali kerana ingin lari dari masalahnya sendiri

programme.title: Secebis Rindu Ep08
programme.desc: Rasya Aleeya dan Syed Reeza berkenalan melalui sistem SMS. Masing-masing tidak ada clue tentang latar belakang atau paras rupa, sekadar bermain kata-kata di skrin telefon bimbit dan laptop sahaja. Pada asalnya mereka berkawan secara suka-suka, namun melalui suara dan kata-kata, maka berkuntum rasa cinta, maka diaturkan pula pertemuan di Kuantan yang akhirnya memekarkan perasaan dua hati dan dua jiwa. Malangnya, sejak dulu lagi Rasya mempunyai penyakit paranoia, sangat bimbang kalau dia ditinggalkan. Dia sentiasa sangsi dengan keikhlasan hati Reeza. Atuk dan opah Rasya di Kampung Ijok pula, sudah lama pasang angan-angan untuk satukan Rasya dengan Fahmi, dua pupu dan rakan sepermainan. Banyak nostalgia lama yang menjadi kenangan bersama Fahmi yang kini merupakan seorang majistret, namun hati Rasya sudah dimilik Reeza seorang arkitek di kota KL. Perasaan paranoid yang menghantui jiwanya, membuatkan Rasya dan Reeza sentiasa bermain tarik-tarik tali. Di suatu sudut, Rasya sangat senang dengan karakter Reeza yang lasak dan aktif, romantis dan budiman. programme.desc: Pengacara Akhmal Nazri dan Atu Zero menjelajah ke Selangor sambil mempromosi beberapa tempat penginapan dilengkapi kemudahan dan aktiviti menarik bagi percutian dan pelancongan. programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep10
programme.desc: Memaparkan Sheila sangat mengharapkan Hani dapat berhubung dengan Nizam kerana Hani sahaja yang akan dilayan panggilan. Hani menelefon Nizam semata-mata kerana harapan Sheila, merayu dia pulang. Sheila berharap dia dapat meminta maaf akibat kesalahannya. Kesempatan Hani berbual, Nizam sering memujuk Hani, menyuarakan segala perasaan dan janji mereka dahulu. Malahan Mizan dengan berkeras hati menyatakan cintanya hanya Hani, bagi Sheila dia tidak sesekali akan memaafkannya. Apabila Hani menyatakan kesetiaan hanyalah kepada suaminya. Nizam sekali lagi bertegas yang dia akan menentukan Mizan tidak menyentuhnya. Hani walau pun seperti berbelah bagi, tetapi dia seorang yang cekal dan tetap taat kepada suaminya. Di sebelah malamnya, Hani terbawa-bawa bagaimana kisah mereka berdua bercinta dahulu. Malahan di satu taman, pernah mereka sama-sama meletakkan "kunci cinta" mereka sebagai janji seia sekata. Suraya masih dengan rakan lelaki yang cuba mencari kerja untuk dia menjadi "modelling". Apa pun melalui jalan pintas Suraya juga bersetuju menjadi pelacur berkelas melalui seorang ahli perniagaan berbangsa Cina. Mizan tidak berapa sihat, kebetulan Hani telah pulang ke rumah. Hani menjagai Mizan dengan sebaiknya. Mizan juga mahukan Hani memanggil dirinya "abang", yang menjadi Hani terasa berlainan. Mereka juga mula keluar bersekali bersantai.

programme.title: Huru Hara S14 Ep02
programme.desc: Di hoskan oleh Anas Ridzuan, Huru Hara kali ini pasti membuatkan anda terhibur sambil bergelak ketawa. Dalam episod ini kita santai bersama barisan artis yang terdiri daripada Siqma, Sherry Ibrahim, Zeppo Youngsterz dan juga kugiran Motherwit.

programme.title: Maria Terindah S1 Ep18
programme.desc: Aris yang bekerja dia Miri, bercadang untuk menghabiskan cuti bersama teman baiknya, Fahad menikmati keindahan alam semulajadi di Hutan Simpan Mulu Sarawak. Sementara itu, Jihan dan Maria yang baru selesai mendaki Gunung Santubong, bercadang untuk melanjutkan percutian mereka ke Mulu sebelum pulang ke Kuala Lumpur. Mereka berempat mula bertemu sewaktu berada di Mulu. Pertemuan pertama kali membuatkan Aris jatuh cinta dengan Maria, dan dalam masa yang sama, menyedari yang Fahad juga menyukai Maria. Malangnya, Jihan dar awal memang tida menyukai dua orang lelaki yang baginya hanya menyusahkan itu. Sepanjang ekspedisi mereka, Jihan yang sentiasa berperanan sebagai seorang kakak nampak kurang senang apabila Maria kerap melayan Aris dan Fahad. Sedikit situasi berlaku di dalam Gua Mulu mengakibatkan Jihan tercedera dan tidak dapat ikut serta pada ekspedisi mereka keesokan hari. Disebabkan terlalu geram dan menyalahkan Fahad atas apa yang berlaku, Fahad juga ditahan dari ikut serta ekspedisi yang akan dijalankan. Akhrinya, hanya Maria dan Aris bersama beberapa orang pengunjung lain yang menyertai ekspedisi tersebut. Di dalam hutan, kerana terlalu teruja dan leka, Maria tersesat dan terpisah dari orang lain. Nasibnya baik kerana Aris ada untuk menyelamatkannya, tetapi mereka akhirnya dapati yang mereka berdua telah sama sama sesat di dalan hutan itu. Aris melindungi Maria sepanjang masa mereka di dalam hutan itu sehingga hari gelap. Dan tiba tiba pada malam hari, mereka diserang dan Aris disumpit.

programme.desc: Haris bingung, apa yang harus dia lakukan. Haris kemudian menyakini dirinya sendiri bahwa apapun yang terjadi dia akan bertanggungjawab atas bayi di perut Riri. programme.title: Mr Wrong Ep31
programme.desc: Ezgi dan zgr, yang kali terakhir bergaduh dan membatalkan perjanjian itu, terkejut apabila mereka mengetahui bahawa mereka akan bekerjasama. programme.title: Transit Terakhir
programme.desc: Khalif seorang anak muda yang sering menghabiskan masa dengan berseronok dan berfoya-foya bersama rakan-rakannya. Khalif juga tidak mempunyai pekerjaan tetap kerana sikapnya yang terlalu memilih kerja. Lantara sikap itulah yang membuatkan kedua-dua orang tuanya iaitu Pak Akob dan Mak Nah begitu kecewa dengan Khalif. Apatah lagi Pak Akob yang telah berusia tetapi masih lagi gigih bekerja untuk menyara keluarga mereka. Pak Akob bekerja sebagai seorang pemandu van jenazah dan dia amat disenangi oleh orang ramai. Dengan pekerjaan itulah dia menyara kehidupan keluarganya. Namun Khalif malu dengan pekerjaan bapanya itu. Selepas ayahnya meninggal dunia, barulah kesedaran mula timbul dalam dirinya kerana terpaksa menjalankan aktiviti bisnes ayahnya.

programme.title: Terowong Ep 7 Ep7
programme.desc: Episod 7,bertajuk ' Mesej Puaka ' ini mengisahkan seorang gadis bernama Dira yang kecewa ditinggalkan kekasihnya mula berkenalan dengan seorang pemuda bernama Aliff melalui SMS. Perhubungan mereka mula intim apabila pada suatu malam Dira dijemput ke rumah Aliff yang terletak di pinggir hutan. Semenjak itu Dira tidak lagi menghiraukan larangan ibunya supaya jangan keluar malam bertemu dengan Aliff. Pada suatu malam Jony (bekas teman lelaki Dira) dan rakan-rakannya yang pergi bertemu Aliff telah mati dibunuh oleh Aliff yang menghisap darah mereka. Tanpa mengetahui identiti Aliff sebenarnya, Dira yang telah dirasuk oleh Aliff sangat teruja dengan lamarannya. Pada suatu malam tanpa menghiraukan larangan kawannya (Watie), Dira yang berpakaian pengantin pergi bertemu dengan Aliff dan Mak Longnya di dalam sebuah terowong untuk melangsungkan perkahwinan mereka. Sebaik sahaja Aliff memeluk Dira, dia terus menghisap darah leher Dira hingga dia pengsan. Apabila Dira sedar,Watie mengajak dia balik tetapi Dira yang telah menjadi pontianak (vampire) seperti Aliff telah ghaib bersama-sama Mak Long ke alam lain.

programme.title: War Of The Arrows
programme.desc: Filem ini bermula dengan dua orang anak, Nam-yi dan adik perempuannya Ja-in, dikejar oleh pengawal Raja Injo dan diselamatkan oleh bapa mereka Choi Pyeong-ryung, seorang pegawai Raja Gwanghae dan seorang pemanah yang mahir. Dia menghantar anak-anaknya untuk mencari tempat perlindungan dengan kawan baiknya Kim Mu-seon. Semasa mereka melarikan diri, Ja-in merayu abangnya untuk kembali kepada bapa mereka, tetapi Choi Pyeong-ryung dibunuh di hadapan Nam-yi. Nam-yi, walaupun digigit oleh anjing pengawal, membunuh mereka dan melarikan diri bersama Ja-in.

Pegawai muda Emilien berazam untuk menyelamatkan duta dan pegawai Petra (teman wanitanya), yang turut diculik, dan memulihkan kehormatan jabatannya. Dengan pembunuh yang tinggal di bilik sebelah, kali ini hantu berlaku bukan dalam satu bilik tetapi dua. Dalam kejutan yang mengejutkan, di antara harta benda si mati, Golok menjumpai keratan akhbar lama yang menggambarkan sebuah keluarga yang hilang di motel berhantu itu, membayangkan bahawa bukan kebetulan mereka terjumpa Losmen Melati pada malam sebelumnya. programme.title: Losmen Melati Ep 5 Ep5
programme.desc: Melati mendedahkan niat sebenar dia yang ingin mengembalikan anaknya dari kematian. Dengan bantuan seorang Bomoh, Watih, Melati akan membawa pulang anaknya menggunakan darah yang dicuri daripada tetamu mudanya yang telah meninggal dunia sebelum ini. Namun, bukan anaknya sahaja yang ingin dibawa pulang. Melati telah membuat keputusan untuk membawa kembali Sigit - lelaki yang dibesarkannya, seorang lelaki yang mempunyai masa lalu yang kelam dan tragis - Melati percaya bahawa di sebalik kengerian masa lalunya, dia layak mendapat peluang kedua. Makhluk jahat yang pernah terperangkap di ruang bawah tanah didedahkan di Kusno, makhluk jahat dan jahat serta bapa Sigit. Apabila Kusno mula membunuh, dia mula menjadi lebih kuat dan mula menyerupai bentuk manusianya sekali lagi. Kusno mempunyai satu misi untuk memusnahkan Melati. Tetapi Kusno tidak bersendirian. Dengan menggunakan kuasanya yang semakin meningkat, dia memihak kepada bentuk jahat lelaki yang membunuh ibu Melati pada tahun 1900-an - Pemburu.

programme.title: Bohsia Jangan Pilih Jalan Hitam
programme.desc: Bohsia: Jangan Pilih Jalan Hitam berkisarkan dua gadis, Tasha (Nabila Huda) dan Amy (Salina Saibi). Tanpa pendidikan tinggi dan didikan yang sewajarnya, kedua-duanya terjebak dalam dunia perlumbaan motor haram - satu keputusan mengubah hidup mereka selama-lamanya.

programme.title: Evolusi KL Drift
programme.desc: Dua orang sahabat, Zack dan Sham berkongsi minat yang sama iaitu perlumbaan kereta drift. Dalam masa yang sama, Zack menjalinkan hubungan cinta dengan Fasha, seorang wanita yang turut mempunyai minat yang mendalam terhadap perlumbaan kereta drift. Walau bagaimanapun, hubungan mereka menjadi semakin dingin kerana Zack sering mengongkong hidup Fasha. Sham cuba untuk mendamaikan mereka berdua tetapi timbul pula bibit-bibit cinta antara dia dengan Fasha.

programme.title: Raja Laut
programme.desc: Para pelaut sering terancam dengan kegiatan seorang lanun bernama Raja Laut yang sering melakukan keganasan. Oleh kerana Raja Laut sangat licik dalam kegiatan haramnya, pihak berkuasa mengalami kesukaran untuk memberkasnya. Dalam masa yang sama, Raja Laut telah menjalinkan hubungan dengan adik seorang pegawai tentera laut yang menyukarkan lagi pihak berkuasa untuk menangkapnya.

programme.title: Sumpah Semerah Padi
programme.desc: Sebuah daerah bernama Semerah Padi berada dalam keadaan aman damai di bawah pemerintahan Demang Satria. Namun, keadaan menjadi kucar kacir apabila Semerah Padi diserang oleh sekumpulan pengganas. Demang Satria mati dibunuh manakala isteri dan anak-anaknya dihalau keluar daripada Semerah Padi. Adi Putera, anak lelaki Demang Satria ialah seorang pemuda yang taat pada agama namun tidak memiliki keberanian untuk mempertahankan diri. Dia menuntut ilmu persilatan dengan Andika. Adi Putera bertekad untuk membalas dendam serta kembali memerintah Semerah Padi dengan ajaran Islam.

programme.title: Lurah Dendam
programme.desc: Sekumpulan ahli payung terjun yang diketuai Kapten Hanafi dalam penerbangan untuk membuat penerjunan di Kuantan. Kapal terbang yang mereka naiki terlanggar seekor burung helang dan mengakibatkan pesawat itu bergegar. Dalam keadaan kelam kabut itu, seorang demi seorang penerjun melompat keluar dan mendarat di sebuah kawasan hutan. Di sana, mereka diganggu pelbagai peristiwa dan menganggap tempat itu berpuaka. programme.title: Evolusi KL Drift
programme.desc: Dua orang sahabat, Zack dan Sham berkongsi minat yang sama iaitu perlumbaan kereta drift. Dalam masa yang sama, Zack menjalinkan hubungan cinta dengan Fasha, seorang wanita yang turut mempunyai minat yang mendalam terhadap perlumbaan kereta drift. Walau bagaimanapun, hubungan mereka menjadi semakin dingin kerana Zack sering mengongkong hidup Fasha. Sham cuba untuk mendamaikan mereka berdua tetapi timbul pula bibit-bibit cinta antara dia dengan Fasha.

Hal ini menimbulkan rasa cemburu Inspektor Aleza namun atas misi menghancurkan dua kumpulan penjenayah itu, dia mengenepikan soal peribadi.

Gadek, orang kanan Tok Kajai sering membuat onar dan cuba menggulingkannya. Pada suatu hari, seorang pemuda bernama Wira datang ke kampung itu dan sering menolong orang-orang yang teraniaya. programme.title: Blessing of Formosa (T) Ep204
programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.title: Keep Rolling
programme.desc: Directorial debut of Man Lim Chung, who spent 3 years filming this documentary about the life and filmmaking philosophy of Ann Hui, one of Hong Kongs greatest filmmakers. It traces Huis life story and her 40-year careers ups and downs using film footages, candid conversations with Hui, and interviews with her collaborators, family and friends.

programme.title: Far Far Away
programme.desc: A 28-year-old IT geek has only been in love once. Surprisingly, he ends up getting romantically involved with five different women this year and the one thing they have in common is that they all live in far flung areas of Hong Kong. After taking five intensive relationship courses within these 365 days, will he find the-one?

programme.title: Schemes in Antiques
programme.desc: Despite his familys expertise in ancient Chinese relics, Xu Yuan becomes an electronics shop owner to distance himself from his disgraced family. However, when an antique is to be returned to China, Xu Yuan uncovers an ancient mystery and soon embarks on a journey that can finally restore his familys reputation but may also cost him his life.

programme.title: The Brotherhood of Rebel
programme.desc: Chai, a triad member, helps his childhood friend Meow flee Hong Kong after discovering that Meow attempted to kill his triad boss. 17 years later, Chai becomes a key member of the triad. When he runs into Meow one day, he knows that his gang will kill Meow if they find him. Caught between triad and brotherhood, what will Chai choose?

programme.title: Lost Love
programme.desc: Mei tries to get over the death of her young son by becoming a foster parent. For 13 years, Meis dedication to the foster child leads her to neglect her husband and the true needs of the child. It is only through the childs unintentional help that the couple finally manages to salvage their relationship.

programme.title: Last Suspect
programme.desc: Lawyer Chen receives a mysterious call demanding her to defend a murder suspect after her daughter is kidnapped, and is told that she can only save her daughter by winning the case. As she starts investigation with the police and evidence emerges, Chen discovers the truth and reveals the mastermind. Can she rescue her daughter in time?

programme.title: American Girl
programme.desc: 13 year-old Fen is uprooted from LA and moves to Taipei in early 2003, when her mother is diagnosed with breast cancer. She struggles to adjust to her new life with a new school and long-separated father, and drifts away from her mother. When her younger sister is misdiagnosed with SARS, they finally open up to each other during quarantine.

programme.title: Treasure Hunt
programme.desc: A commercial director Peggy shoots an ad on a deserted island while some mysterious men with the treasure map are also there to hunt for the hidden Ming Dynasty treasures. However, the map is stolen by Star who lives on the island. Star and Peggy unveil the hidden treasures but end up being chased by the mysterious men

programme.title: The Sunny Side of the Street
programme.desc: Hassan is a Pakistani refugee boy whose father has died in a car accident. A local taxi driver, Yat, then helps him flee Hong Kong. In the process, the two gradually develop a father-son relationship, until Hassan discovers the shocking truth about his fathers death

programme.title: Wolf Hiding
programme.desc: A cold-blooded killer, Chen An vows to take revenge for her sister who was killed by a crime gang. Dealing with the police and the triad at the same time, a final battle between good and evil has just begun!

programme.title: Once Upon a Time in Shanghai
programme.desc: Ma Yong Zhen moves to Shanghai in the hope of becoming rich but ends up having to use his kung fu skills to survive and take revenge against the gang who killed his brother.

programme.title: A Cool Fish
programme.desc: In this dark-comedy, cop-turned-security guard Ma faces the ultimate challenge when his boss mysteriously disappears and his paralyzed sister makes a morbid deal with the armed bandits who abduct her.

programme.title: Echoes of the Thunder
programme.desc: Two half-brothers, Nam and Fire, are top racing drivers. In a racing challenge with Japanese driver Kenji, Nam causes a young racing driver to be seriously injured and is depressed. Fire stands up for Nam and decides to compete with Kenji in an illegal street car race. Who will win the race? Can Nam finally bounce back?

programme.title: Sex and the Beauties
programme.desc: It is said that Hong Kong is a sexy and sexual city where life is breathtakingly fast but glamorous. Fear of marriage, single & successful psychiatrist, Selina and other beauties seek for love and happy endings.

programme.title: A Witness out of the Blue
programme.desc: The police suspects that a jewel thief, found dead in his unit with all stolen goods missing, is killed by his gang leader. They also found the crime to be related to a jewel robbery many months ago, with the robbers involved being killed off one by one. In this complicated case, the polices only witness is a talking parrot from the crime scene.

programme.title: July Rhapsody
programme.desc: A 40-year-old high school teacher is in midlife crisis, his marriage is on the rocks and he is involved in a taboo romance with a female student who has a crush on him. Meanwhile, his wife is off to care for her dying ex-lover who shares a complicated history with the couple...

programme.title: Hell Hole
programme.desc: The movie features three horror stories in different era: a pregnant woman haunted by a ghost sacrifices her life to save her baby; a boy commits suicide after being bullied by four medical students and his spirit returns for revenge; some company staff are haunted after they open a box of used clothes, releasing a more than 20-year resentment.

programme.title: Cloudy Mountain
programme.desc: When a decade-long tunnel project is about to complete, an earthquake strikes and leads to a series of subsidence and landslides. The tunnel and a nearby town are at stake. A retired soldier and his son step up to try and stop the disasters at source. Will the authority decide to blow up the tunnel to save the 160,000 people in town?

programme.title: Golden Chicken 2
programme.desc: The sequel is set in 2046 when a 82-year-old Ah Kam stops a heartbroken young man from taking memory loss pills. To help ease his pain, Ah Kam shares her life stories from 2003, one of Hong Kongs toughest year with SARS, including the different people she comes across and the bittersweet romance between herself and her cousin.

programme.title: Come Back Home
programme.desc: In a chilly winter, De and his family goes on a self-drive tour to Changbai Mountain. The holiday turns tragic when Des eight-year-old son goes missing. He seeks help from the local police but is unable to find his son. Though the golden hour has passed, De and the rescue team insist on continuing the search. Can they finally rescue the boy?

programme.title: New Police Story
programme.desc: Senior Inspector Wing is an elite in the police force but has been drowning his guilt in booze after his entire team was killed by the Gang of Five in a mission. A year later, a young rookie detective with a complicated background is assigned to partner Wing and manages to inspire him into action, as Wing vows to take down the gang.

programme.title: Flirting Scholar from the Future
programme.desc: Tiger, Lambert and Skinny Pig are massive fans of the movie, Flirting Scholar. One day, Skinny Pig who is an obscure inventor, puts together a movie time machine and accidentally sucks all of them into the movie of Flirting Scholar. The trio head off to Wah mansion to meet the maid Autumn can they find her and can they return to the present?

programme.title: Kill Mobile
programme.desc: Seven friends get together and decide to play a game where they must share all the messages, calls and app notifications on each other's cell phones. Hilarity and drama follows as everyone's secrets are unveiled throughout the evening, and the seven friends find themselves more like strangers to each other than ever before!

programme.title: Cliff Walkers
programme.desc: The first spy thriller movie by famous Director Zhang Yi Mou, this film follows four Communist Party special agents who embark on a secret operation in the Japanese puppet state of Manchukuo in 1932. Sold out by a traitor, the agents, who split up into two teams, find themselves surrounded by threats on all sides. Can they complete their mission?

programme.title: The Silent War
programme.desc: After the Chinese Civil War, 701 Bureau continues to monitor the coded transmissions between rebel forces. When radio frequencies used by the opponent disappear suddenly, Agent Zhang asks Ho, a blind piano tuner with exceptional hearing, to help find the transmission signals. Can Ho find the missing signals and foil a possible assassination plot?

programme.title: Dearest Anita
programme.desc: Based on real events, the movie follows the footsteps of the fans of Hong Kong Canto-pop diva Anita Mui. After the death of the popstar, fans from different walks of life risk arrest to track down handwritten cards, letters and other possessions from Anita Mui to preserve their idols memory.

programme.title: The Brotherhood of Rebel
programme.desc: Chai, a triad member, helps his childhood friend Meow flee Hong Kong after discovering that Meow attempted to kill his triad boss. 17 years later, Chai becomes a key member of the triad. When he runs into Meow one day, he knows that his gang will kill Meow if they find him. Caught between triad and brotherhood, what will Chai choose?

programme.title: Kung Fu Dunk
programme.desc: Shi Jie grew up in a martial arts school and possesses an extraordinary shooting skill. Street hustler Chen Li sees his talent and arranges for him to join a university basketball team. With his kung fu dunking skill, Shi Jie manages to win all college basketball matches, bringing him wealth and also strengthening his relationship with Chen Li.

programme.title: The Grand Grandmaster
programme.desc: Ma Fei Lung, a Chinese martial arts grandmaster, lost everything after he is floored by a former female boxing champion, Chan Tsang. The relevant video was posted on social media and he became the laughing stock of everyone. To reclaim his reputation, Fei Lung challenges Chan Tsang to a rematch. Who will be the winner?

programme.title: Summer Heat
programme.desc: Aptly described by its original title of "Money, Sex And Love", this is a gripping drama about Judy, a woman with a rich husband as well as two lovers who happen to be brothers. Jenny Hu is Judy, and her knockout beauty makes this summer sizzle...

programme.title: Return Of The One-Armed Swordsman
programme.desc: One-armed Swordsman Fang Kang wants to lead a quiet life with his wife, but when she is abducted by the Eight Demon Swordsmen clan, he is forced to take them on in order to save her.

programme.title: Human Lanterns
programme.desc: Zhao was once defeated by Long in a duel. 7 years later, Long asks Zhao to make a unique lantern on his behalf to win the lantern contest, while Zhao plans for revenge. When Longs wife suddenly disappears one day and he hears about the story of human lanterns, Long suspects Zhao may be involved in the incident

programme.title: The Golden Lion
programme.desc: The Golden Lion is a bandit with good martial arts skills and often robs from the rich to help the poor. He is ambushed and attacked by a gang one night but luckily found help from a master healer, who has to find a way to treat him while they are both being chased by the gang.

programme.title: The Last Tempest
programme.desc: This sequel to The Empress Dowager continues the tale of Emperor Guangxu and Empress Dowager Cixi. Despite Guangxus enthronement, his ability to rule effectively is overshadowed by the ever-present power of Cixi. When his attempts to reform the Imperial system are thwarted by the Empress Dowager, Guangxu attempts to curb her power.

programme.title: Lion Vs Lion
programme.desc: The traditional lion dance has never looked so good as in Lion VS Lion which captures the most impressive sequences of lion dancing on film. Besides being loaded with enjoyable martial arts chicanery, film historians can revel because it's also the first film that clearly demonstrates the intricacies and differences between the traditional Northern and Southern lion dancing techniques. The Five Venom alumnus and Chang Cheh discovery, Lo Meng, teams up with Liu Chia-liang protege Wang Yu, as they inadvertently turn from vagabond kung-fu school operators into anti-Ching, patriotic fighters.

programme.title: My Son
programme.desc: Kuo, a polices son, blames his father for his mothers death. He has no job, spends time in night clubs and always gets into fights. One night, Kuo rescues Mei from being raped and they become friends. Kuo wants to support Mei and her family so he goes gambling hoping to gain more money but bad luck seems to be following them with tragic outcomes.

programme.title: Journey Of The Doomed
programme.desc: Journey Of The Doomed stars Tung Wei as a knight that finds himself protecting the life of a beautiful young lady, the lost Emperor's daughter and stalked by a bunch of assassins headed by kung fu actress extraordinaire Hui Ying-Hung.

programme.title: The Merry Wife
programme.desc: A 17-year old schoolgirl marries her 35-year-old teacher. Comedy ensues when they attempt to keep their relationship a secret despite being in the same school. When they discover unwanted suitors going after their other halves, jealousy threatens to expose their marriage any minute!

programme.title: The Master Of Kung Fu
programme.desc: The famous kung fu master Wong Fei Hung teaches martial arts in Guangdong. A vicious gangster plots to harm Wongs disciples and frames him for robbery and murder. Wong has to fight against the culprit to prove his own innocence and take revenge for his disciples.

programme.title: Bloody Parrot
programme.desc: A swordsman is suspected of being the thief of a treasure sent to Emperor. Through his investigation, he is led on to the trail of the supernatural Bloody Parrot. Poisonous things happen including a demonic possession, witches casting poison spells and disgusting autopsies. Then a dead constable turns into a vampire!

programme.title: Asia-Pol
programme.desc: Asiapol agent Yang Ming Xuan trails a shipment of contraband gold being delivered to gang leader, George Eaton. He enlists the help of a Chinese woman who is trying to avenge her sister and narrowly escapes several deadly traps as he closes in on Eaton's location. This spy film is loosely inspired by the James Bond movies.

programme.title: Gang Master
programme.desc: This is a story about an army out to destroy the Hsien Lung gang of anti-Yuan revolutionaries. Their leader Ru Yi Tu is up against Fu Zhong Yuan, the identified successor of the Hsien Lung gang who must also prove his own legitimacy. The plot thickens with murder, sibling rivalry and shocking discoveries that could change the course of history.

programme.title: Carry On Doctors And Nurses
programme.desc: At St. Morant Hospital, a harried but lovely administrator must deal with lusty interns, student nurses, a delirious surgeon, a dissection fiend, a criticizing Commissioner and gross negligence at regular intervals! This comedy is based on the hugely successful British Carry On! film series.

programme.title: Usurpers Of Emperor'S Power
programme.desc: The last ruler of Tang, Li Yao is deposed by Chao Kuang-jun, the founder of the Sung Dynasty. Unfortunately his actions unleash a new plague - his brother Kuang-yi - on the courts and his people. The marauding Kuang-yi rapes and plunders. As more people get involved, it turns into a bloody battlefield of betrayal. It is up to upright officials like Li Lang to put an end to it. But can one man take on the imperial army?

programme.title: Song Of Orchid Island
programme.desc: Dr. He moves to the remote Lanyu island off the coast of Taiwan to look for his long lost father, and starts to run a clinic curing islanders who are bitten by the fatal red worms there. He meets Ya Lan who works as a nurse in his clinic and falls in love with him. Things get vicious for Dr. He as a jealous islander plots to get rid of him

programme.title: Perils Of The Sentimental Swordsman
programme.desc: The titanic team of Director Chu Yuan and Novelist Ku Lung chose to give their hero (Ti Lung) a whole new cliffhanger-fraught adventure featuring a mysterious swordsman, a sensual swordswoman, an imperial assassin, a ghost mansion, a booby-trapped tunnel, as well as double crosses and secret missions.

programme.title: The Imperial Tomb Raiders
programme.desc: The story revolves around a maverick, a band of woman warriors and a group of ruthless bandits. The maverick teams up with the woman warriors to battle the bandits seeking to raid the emperors tomb.

programme.title: The Warlord
programme.desc: A bandit became a warlord in northern China by helping Russia fight against Japan. Due to his ignorance and silly behaviour, he is seen as a joke to everyone. The warlord is finally killed by the daughter of a troupe master whom he had killed for no reason, bringing a befitting end to a traitor.

programme.title: Crazy Nuts Of Kung Fu
programme.desc: A roadside bandit and a traveling gambler team up to make money from gambling. In a successful attempt to steal a huge amount of money from a warlords home, they encounter revolutionists who seek their help to fund the reform campaign. Will the two help the revolutionists cause with the stolen money?

programme.title: Dawn Will Come
programme.desc: Liang Cai drugged the beautiful Qiu Rong and raped her, but promised to marry her after getting his parents consent. Since then, there is no news of his proposal and Qiu Rong confronts Liang Cai when she finds herself pregnant. This is when she discovers that he has already married a rich noble girl and even plans to kill her

programme.title: Martial Club
programme.desc: The young Wong Fei Hung and his friend Wang Yin Lin offend the young master of another rival school and the expert they hire, causing both martial arts schools to fight against each other. This is Director Liu Chia Liangs masterpiece and one of the top ten highest grossing movies in 1981.

programme.title: Tropicana Interlude
programme.desc: Ping and Su are lovers who operate a travel agency specializing in Southeast Asian holidays. Tung, a school mistress, and her students join a guided tour lead by Ping. During the trip, a spoiled kid Li is attracted to Ping but Su thinks Ping has fallen for Tung and leaves. How will Ping deal with the situation and ends up happily back with Su?

programme.title: The Thunderbolt Fist
programme.desc: A vicious Japanese judo expert wants to prove that Chinese are the sick people of Asia and sets out to sabotage and kill the best martial artists in dangerous tournaments. To save his son from this, the head of Ping Pai Boxing Institute sends him to the mountains to learn the powerful Thunderbolt Fist technique from master fighter, Red Butterfly.

programme.title: The Purple Shell
programme.desc: Hui and Ha are stuck in their unhappy marriages and are attracted to each other when they meet at a party. In one of their beach strolls, Ha picks up a purple shell and gives it to Hui as a memento. When Huis husband finds out about them, he hurts Hui and cause her to become seriously ill, while also blackmails Ha. How will this love story end?

programme.title: Heads For Sale
programme.desc: Hua is an upright and brave swordswoman who will stand up against villains and do anything for Luo, the man she loves. When Luo is sent to jail by the corrupted police, she sets out to free him and did not hesitate to chop off two bodyguards heads. In the process, she also stumbles across an old enemy of her father who is back seeking revenge.

programme.title: The Imperial Swordsman
programme.desc: Fu is a government officer heading home after being charged with falsifying reports. En route, he encounters & recruits a skilled swordsman as a bodyguard. They then meet a fleeing bride and her maid who asked to join them for protection. When the group reach a ruined temple however, a gang of assassins appear and attack them

programme.title: Little Dragon Maiden
programme.desc: With Hong Kong cinema's new wave, high flying, martial arts action of the 1980's, came a new wave of actors; teeny-bopper, canto-pop singer/stars with little or no martial arts background. However, when a film like LITTLE DRAGON MAIDEN intelligently mixes the old with the new, the results are pure golden magic. This costume-action, drama, love story features relative newcomer Leslie Cheung, who falls in love with the Dragon Maiden while learning the art of swordplay. The recipe is complete when veteran kung-fu stars Chen Kuan-tai and Lo Lieh add just enough weapon-wielding spice to make this film really cook. Cheung garnered international recognition in John Woo's A BETTER TOMORROW and Ronny Yu's THE BRIDE WITH WHITE HAIR.

programme.title: The Kingdom And The Beauty
programme.desc: Emperor Cheng Te meets country maiden Li Feng on a visit to Southern China. It was love at first sight and the Emperor leaves with a promise that Li Feng would be his empress. When he sends for Li one year later, she was too ill to withstand the arduous journey and arrives just in time to die in the arms of her beloved...

programme.title: The Flag Of Iron
programme.desc: When super director Chang Cheh found new talent and blood with "The Five Venoms" actors, most of which were trained in the highly acrobatic Chinese opera and well versed with exotic martial arts weapons, this created a new spark for his use of bizarre weapons in his films. The Flag Of Iron is one of 20 movies that he directed featuring the utterly flabbergasting and physically exhausting action bits created by these five dudes. You have the good guys from the righteous clan versus the bad guys from the villainous clan and it's so filled with "don't-blink-or-you-will-miss-something" gags, you will need to watch it over and over again so you can see the things you missed.

programme.title: Na Cha The Great
programme.desc: Adapted from a chapter of the classic Chinese legend Investiture of the Gods, this is the story of Na Cha set 3000 years ago. After Na Cha sacrificed his life to save his parents, he is reincarnated with his spirit embodied in a lotus flower and is armed with two magic weapons to save the people from their despotic emperor.

programme.title: New Tales Of The Flying Fox
programme.desc: In a great rendition of The Silver Fox and Legend of the Fox comes this exciting adventure, where the only thing between the clan leaders and certain death is Hui Ying-hung.

programme.title: The Amorous Lotus Pan
programme.desc: Adapted from the renowned Chinese novel, The Water Margin, this is the story of a poor and beautiful girl Lotus Pan, who is raped by her master and had to be married off to a midget who treats her badly. Lost and lonely, Pan unwittingly becomes a pawn in the game of lust between her husbands playboy brother Wu Song, and a murderous man Men Ching.

programme.title: Raw Courage
programme.desc: After the Ming Emperor is overthrown and his infant son was put in the care of the Black Dragon Society, a traitorous martial arts clan attacks the society, forcing an inexperienced pair of swordsman and swordswoman to flee with the infant. Their journey to deliver the infant to safety is filled with dangers that would require help from other allies

programme.title: The Snake Prince
programme.desc: The Snake Prince lives on the Snake Mountain of Kwangsi with other snakes and they have lived peacefully with humans for a thousand years. All things change however, when the Snake Prince falls in love with one of the three beauties performing a sensual rain dance in the nearby village one day, and decides to marry her at all costs...

programme.title: Two Champions Of Shaolin
programme.desc: Set in the Qing Dynasty, the Shaolin clan wants to overthrow Qing and restore the Ming Dynasty, while the Wudang clan is backed by the Qing government. The two renowned clans eventually set themselves up against each other, and a series of vicious fighting has just begun

programme.title: Sucker Punch
programme.desc: Close your eyes. Open your mind. You will be unprepared. From the Spartan slaughter of 300 to the visionary world of Watchmen, writer/director/producer Zack Snyder has transported audiences into visual dreamscapes of his creation. His latest cinematic mind trip takes us into the vivid imagination of a young girl (The Uninvited's Emily Browning) whose dream world provides the ultimate escape from her darker institutionalized reality. Unrestrained by the boundaries of time and place, she is free to go where her mind takes her, but her incredible adventures blur the lines between what's real and what is imaginary. Locked away against her will, but determined to fight for her freedom, she and four other girls battle everything from serpents tosamurais on an unbelievable journey to set themselves free. Like "Alice in Wonderland with machine guns," Snyder's epic action fantasy is filmed in such a way that the action sequences aren't limited by physical real...
